	<item>
		<title>Event Apps: How the stats and figures underline their important to event sucess</title>
		<link>https://micepad.co/hk/blog/event-apps-how-the-stats-and-figures-underline-their-important-to-event-sucess</link>
					<comments>https://micepad.co/hk/blog/event-apps-how-the-stats-and-figures-underline-their-important-to-event-sucess#respond</comments>
		
